            "valueString": "D2393 CONDITIONAL APPROVAL SATISFIED: Clinical examination at crown preparation (2026-07-15) confirmed less than 40% remaining coronal tooth structure on Tooth #3 following endodontic access and caries excavation. Core buildup with resin composite placed to restore adequate retention form for crown. Clinical narrative: 'Endodontically treated 2026-06-17. Estimated 35% coronal structure remaining. Buildup required for crown retention.' Post-obturation periapical on file confirms successful obturation. Authorization ANT-PREAUTH-2026-JNG001 line 3 condition satisfied.",
