            },
            "valueString": "Crown seat date: 2026-07-15. Crown type: Porcelain/ceramic (all-ceramic). Lab case reference: HFD-LAB-2026-0715-003. No prior crown on Tooth #3 on record. Plan frequency limitation (1 crown per tooth per 5 years) satisfied."
